        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: only include the current changelog section in tarball",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Keep the repository `CHANGELOG.md` cumulative, including `Unreleased`, and package only the relevant release section during npm prepack and the shared Docker/package-acceptance package builder.\n- Add a `scripts/package-changelog.mjs` helper that backs up the source changelog, selects the package version's exact stable/correction/prerelease section, falls back from prerelease to stable and then `Unreleased`, and restores the source changelog on `postpack`, the next prepack, or the ignore-scripts package-builder path.\n- Fail closed if the packaged changelog would exceed 500 KB, so parser mistakes cannot silently ship a huge release artifact.\n- Cover stable, correction, alpha/beta, fallback, missing-section, oversized-output, prepare/restore behavior, ignore-scripts builder ordering, and restore-on-pack-failure behavior in focused tests.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node_modules/.bin/oxfmt --check --threads=1 scripts/package-openclaw-for-docker.mjs test/scripts/package-openclaw-for-docker.test.ts scripts/package-changelog.mjs test/scripts/package-changelog.test.ts scripts/openclaw-prepack.ts package.json && node --check scripts/package-changelog.mjs && node --check scripts/package-openclaw-for-docker.mjs && node --check scripts/openclaw-prepack.ts && git diff --check`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/scripts/package-changelog.test.ts test/scripts/package-openclaw-for-docker.test.ts` (`2 passed`, `15 passed`)\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --prompt <packaging lifecycle review prompt>` (`autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`)\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --prompt <incremental template refactor and 500 KB fail-safe review prompt>` (`autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`)\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local --prompt <ignore-scripts builder and signal-safe restore review prompt>` (`autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`)\n\n## Package Proof\n\nGenerated real npm tarballs from the same checkout with `--ignore-scripts`; the only input difference was whether `CHANGELOG.md` had been prepared by `scripts/package-changelog.mjs` before packing.\n\nCommands:\n\n```sh\nnpm pack --ignore-scripts --json --pack-destination \"$full_dir\"\nnode scripts/package-changelog.mjs prepare\nnpm pack --ignore-scripts --json --pack-destination \"$trim_dir\"\nnode scripts/package-changelog.mjs restore\n```\n\nResults:\n\n| Pack input | Tarball size | Unpacked size | `CHANGELOG.md` size | Entry count |\n| --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: |\n| Full source changelog | 3,022,740 bytes | 9,927,030 bytes | 2,399,938 bytes | 798 |\n| Packaged current-section changelog | 2,198,753 bytes | 7,533,506 bytes | 6,414 bytes | 798 |\n\n- `CHANGELOG.md` reduction: **2,393,524 bytes** (**99.73% smaller**)\n- Whole `.tgz` reduction: **823,987 bytes** (**27.26% smaller**)\n- Whole unpacked package reduction: **2,393,524 bytes** (**24.11% smaller**)\n- Restore proof: after `node scripts/package-changelog.mjs restore`, source `CHANGELOG.md` returned to `sha256=7abb77d14941d7c1b542d1a04f2010dbd91eeb2826849585c6afbb05e9c96c62`\n",
